The man known as General within a villainous organization that plans to take over the world is usually fighting to the death against the Rangers who protect the Earth...
But today is his day off.
To heal his tired soul from working so hard every day, he goes to the zoo to see pandas and to the convenience store to get some ice cream.
We get to see how a certain villain gets to completely enjoy his days off to the fullest in this comedy that will heal your soul.
(Source: Crunchyroll)

Maomao lived a peaceful life with her apothecary father. Until one day, shes sold as a lowly servant to the emperors palace. But she wasnt meant for a compliant life among royalty. So when imperial heirs fall ill, she decides to step in and find a cure! This catches the eye of Jinshi, a handsome palace official who promotes her. Now, shes making a name for herself solving medical mysteries!
(Source: Crunchyroll)

Making up for her sins in a past life as the evil princess Elise, Aoi Takamoto dedicates her life to saving people as a doctor. But a fatal accident cuts her atonement short and suddenly shes back to her previous life, 10 years before her death! Will her foresight and medical brilliance help her change her past ways and heal an ailing empire, or is fate doomed to repeat itself?
(Source: Crunchyroll)

Yuki Itose is just a typical student dealing with the pressures of college. She is struggling one day on the train when an upperclassman named Itsuomi Nagi helps her out. As he gradually opens a new world to her, Yuki develops feelings for Itsuomi. A pure love story begins to grow.
(Source: Crunchyroll)
